Products.Name: Masterfoods Chilli Powder Mexican
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Masterfoods Chilli Powder Mexican' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
A Mexican-inspired blend including paprika, chilli, cumin and garlic. Stir into beef or bean mixes to create delicious family meals.
Add a kick of chilli to your midweek meals with MasterFoods™ Mexican Chilli Powder. A savoury herb with a floral aroma and slightly warming peppermint aftertaste. A blend inspired by the flavours of Mexico, made with paprika, cumin, chilli and garlic. Stir through beef or bean mix and enjoy delicious tacos, enchiladas, burritos or chilli con carne. For something different, sprinkle over your favourite meat before barbecuing for a delicious addition of flavour.
Blended with MasterFoods™ Herbs & Spices
Grown with Integrity, sourced with Pride.
Medium Heat
